## Project Members [/projects/{projectId}/members]
+ Parameters
    + projectId: proj456 (string, required) - The unique project identifier

### List project members [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Developer])

### Add a member [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (MemberAdd)

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Developer)

### Remove a member [DELETE /projects/{projectId}/members/{developerId}]
+ Parameters
    + projectId: proj456 (string, required) - The unique project identifier
    + developerId: dev123 (string, required) - The developer ID to remove

+ Response 204

